<main class="main self-registration">

    <span class="self-registration__graphism graphism-circle"></span>
    <img class="self-registration__img" src="/assets/img/img-autocadastro-login.png"
        alt="Três pessoas sorrindo: uma professora negra, uma aluna pre-adolescente e um aluno do infantil.">

    <div class="row m-bottom--xl m-top--xxl middle-xs">
        <div class="col-xs-5 col-md-3">
            {{programa-semente-logo class="logo"}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <form autocomplete="off" class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
            <p>Para iniciar seu cadastro, por favor defina um login e uma senha para você.</p>
            <div id="form-login" class="form-group m-top--lg w100" autocomplete="off">
                <label class="form-group__label" for="login" maxlength="100">Nome de usuário</label>
                <div class="form-group__input-container form-group__input-container--has-validation">
                    <input  class="form-group__input w100"
                            autocomplete="new-user"
                            autofocus
                            id="login"
                            onblur={{action 'verifyEmail'}}
                            onkeydown={{action 'liveCheckEmail'}}
                            type="text">
                </div>
                {{!-- <span id='login-error'></span> --}}
                <p class="alert alert--sm alert--error alert--has-icon m-top--sm animated d250" id="login-error"
                    data-animation="fadeIn">
                    <span class="alert__icon icon-x"></span>
                    <span class="alert__msg"></span>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group m-top--md w100">
                <label class="form-group__label" for="senha">Senha</label>
                <input class="form-group__input" type="password" id="senha" onkeyup={{action 'verifyPassword'}} onblur={{action 'verifyPassword'}} autocomplete="new-password">
                <span id='password-error'></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group m-top--sm w100">
                <label class="form-group__label" for="senha">Repetir Senha</label>
                <input class="form-group__input" type="password" id="senha2" onkeyup={{action 'verifyPassword'}} onblur={{action 'verifyPassword'}}>
                <p class="alert alert--sm alert--error alert--has-icon m-top--sm animated d250" id="pass-error"
                    data-animation="fadeIn">
                    <span class="alert__icon icon-x"></span>
                    <span class="alert__msg"></span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <button class="btn btn--md m-top--lg" dataDisabled="true" id='submit' type="button"
                onclick={{action 'createUser'}}>Avançar</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
